key_metrics.Average: Average of the three main scores: (Call Rejection Classification Accuracy + FC + Plan) / 3
key_metrics.Call Rejection Classification Accuracy: (reject_f1 + fc_f1) / 2 - Average F1 score for rejection and FC classification
key_metrics.FC: (function_name_f1 + arguments_key_f1 + arguments_value_f1) / 3 - Function call quality score
key_metrics.Plan: Overall workflow score including failures - workflow_evaluation_with_failure

workflow_scores.workflow_evaluation_without_failure: Overall workflow score excluding workflow generation failures
workflow_scores.average_structural_GED: Workflow structure GED score (1-GED, higher is better)
workflow_scores.average_component_GED: Workflow component GED score (1-GED, higher is better)

function_call_scores.total_function_call_cases: Total number of function call cases

reject_decision_performance.f1: F1 score for rejection decision performance
reject_decision_performance.accuracy: (TP_reject + TN_reject) / (TP + TN + FP + FN) - Rejection decision accuracy

fc_decision_performance.precision: FC_TP / (FC_TP + FC_FP) - Function call decision precision
fc_decision_performance.recall: FC_TP / (FC_TP + FC_FN) - Function call decision recall
fc_decision_performance.f1: F1 score for function call decision performance
fc_decision_performance.accuracy: (FC_TP + FC_TN) / (FC_TP + FC_FP + FC_FN + FC_TN) - FC decision accuracy

error_patterns.underaction_rate: Rate of missed necessary actions (FP_reject / total_errors)

call_rejection_scores.rejection_type_accuracy: (TP_reject - type_mismatch) / TP_reject - How often rejection type was correct
call_rejection_scores.total_rejection_type_mismatch: Count of cases where model correctly rejected but with wrong type
call_rejection_scores.total_failed_generation: Count of cases where model failed to generate valid prediction

raw_confusion_matrix.total_true_positive_fc: FC True Positive - Actual FC, Predicted FC
raw_confusion_matrix.total_false_positive_fc: FC False Positive - Actual reject, Predicted FC
raw_confusion_matrix.total_false_negative_fc: FC False Negative - Actual FC, Predicted reject
raw_confusion_matrix.total_true_negative_fc: FC True Negative - Actual reject, Predicted reject
